{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6042", "repo": "rails", "body": "In last commit I've fixed two things.\r\nFirst one is return old value from cache after object changes:\r\n```\r\nbarney.address.street // => \"Quiet Road\"\r\nbarney.address_street = \"Noisy Road\"\r\nbarney.address.street // => \"Quiet Road\" but should be \"Noisy Road\"\r\n```\r\nand another one with type conversion (related to #2084):\r\n```\r\nbarney.address = Address.new(\"May Street\", \"Chicago\", \"USA\", \"31\")\t\r\nbarney.address_house_number // => 31\r\nbarney.address.house_number // => \"31\" but should be 31\r\n```\r\nNow it works how it should work, in my opinion. Wdyt @josevalim ?", "_id": {"$oid": "52380fc1bd3543c15100d58c"}, "issue_id": 6042, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5436975", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6042#issuecomment-5436975", "updated_at": "2012-05-01T11:19:45Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech", "login": "edtsech", "gravatar_id": "ceb745dc6fd0e274005d8c9637cca631", "html_url": "https://github.com/edtsech", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/ceb745dc6fd0e274005d8c9637cca631?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc15ea64280d86e70394c5ffa6c9fa373.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 118158, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/edtsech/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-05-01T11:19:45Z", "id":